---
title: Honey-Thyme Haloumi, Prawns & Roast Pumpkin with Roast Veggie Toss & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Tossing everything together is a lot of fun and allows for all the flavours to melt into each other. For example, this roasted pumpkin sprinkled in Nan’s special seasoning combines with prawns and herby veggies to form the ultimate combo. The salty haloumi balances out the veggies perfectly. An easy win for a weeknight dinner.
